MODIFICATIONS

This version has been modified from the original Raspberry Pi Imager with
the following key changes:

1. Rebranded user interface from "Raspberry Pi Imager" to "ZimaOS USB Creator"
2. Updated application metadata and descriptions for ZimaOS
3. Modified translations and localization files
4. Customized for ZimaOS ecosystem integration

All modifications are licensed under the same Apache License 2.0 as the
original work.

For a complete list of changes, please refer to the git commit history at:
https://github.com/IceWhaleTech/ZimaOS-USB-Creator

